Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini, kita bisa duel tanpa gangguan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.24,0:00:09.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini maumu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.08,0:00:13.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih baik begini daripada\Nmati terkubur dalam tanah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.96,0:00:16.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setidaknya, jasadmu akan\Nkubaringkan menghadap langit.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak tahu yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.22,0:00:28.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi bulan lebih indah, kini tertutup awan.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.56,0:00:29.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.02,0:00:32.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei! Setidaknya dengarkan aku dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.73,0:00:33.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak perlu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.65,0:00:38.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau repot-repot naik ke sini\Nbukan cuma untuk bicara, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:39.11,0:00:41.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dugaanmu salah!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.32,0:00:42.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini salah paham!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.32,0:00:44.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salah paham?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.57,0:00:47.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enteng sekali bicaramu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.87,0:00:50.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membakar rumah sakit.\NItu salah paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.29,0:00:53.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mencoba membunuh anak kecil.\NItu juga salah paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.54,0:00:58.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membunuh para preman itu.\NSemuanya salah paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.88,0:01:00.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengejekku?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.71,0:01:02.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asal tahu saja, bukan begitu kejadiannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mencoba menghentikannya!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.72,0:01:08.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi saat aku tiba,\Nsemuanya sudah terlambat!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.05,0:01:14.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyuruhku memantau,\Nlalu turun tangan di saat genting...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:15.48,0:01:22.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaiknya aku sedikit mendekat.\NTapi jika kulakukan, pasti ketahuan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bocah itu, Mikado,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.32,0:01:29.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,punya indra yang sangat tajam,\Nbagai binatang.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.41,0:01:36.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku turun tangan sekarang,\Naku takkan lolos tanpa luka.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.21,0:01:40.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak itu benar-benar kuat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.26,0:03:19.68,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Tiap perbuatanmu membuktikan\Nkau memang bersalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.35,0:03:23.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mencoba\Nmemercayaimu sepenuh hati.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.94,0:03:27.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai malam itu,\Nsaat aku melihatmu di markas mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengarkan dulu penjelasanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.82,0:03:29.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.74,0:03:40.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa bodoh karena memercayaimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.17,0:03:48.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, yang paling membuatku kesal\Nadalah kau memanfaatkanku
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk membunuh anak-anak dan preman!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.18,0:03:55.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mempermainkan perasaan orang,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,itu dosa yang keji.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.56,0:04:07.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yamata no Orochi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat, dia keluarkan senjatanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, Mikado! Aku belum selesai bicara!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.16,0:04:21.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tembakanku sengaja kubuat meleset.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang perlu kau lakukan sebelum mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.17,0:04:27.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertobat dan akuilah dosamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.21,0:04:30.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bawa kebohonganmu ke liang kubur.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.67,0:04:32.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mau!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.34,0:04:33.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan minta maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak salah, buat apa minta maaf?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.51,0:04:38.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengecewakanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.12,0:05:03.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia serius ingin membunuhku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.12,0:05:07.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus kutenangkan dia,\Natau akan ada pertumpahan darah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.21,0:05:10.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.05,0:05:18.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat malam festival, kau mendekatiku\Nkarena tahu aku Momotaro?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ha?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.06,0:05:27.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setiap kata yang keluar dari mulutmu,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.06,0:05:29.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,kini terdengar seperti kebohongan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.69,0:05:36.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya sudah terlambat.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.11,0:05:42.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pun mulai meragukan pertemuan kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham kenapa dia ragu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.79,0:05:51.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi apa dia sungguh\Ntak percaya padaku sedikit pun?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.88,0:05:55.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.05,0:05:57.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.26,0:06:06.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagimu, aku bukan lagi teman,\Nmelainkan musuhmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertobatlah di neraka.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.07,0:06:16.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya sudah, baiklah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.08,0:06:26.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak berniat untuk mendengarkanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.91,0:06:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kubuat kau mendengarkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.13,0:06:33.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teknik Gerhana Darah!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.38,0:06:38.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau harus memaksa agar kau mau mendengar,\Nakan kulakukan!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.06,0:06:53.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bodoh!\NBerani sekali kau mendekatiku begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.02,0:06:57.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mustahil. Tidak mungkin!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya tidak begini!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.11,0:07:02.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak percaya ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi bohong!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.66,0:07:10.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Matilah, Bodoh!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.42,0:07:19.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupasang bom kecil di beberapa ubin ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ledakannya cukup kecil agar tak melukaiku,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.05,0:07:24.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi cukup besar untuk hancurkan kakinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.14,0:07:27.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingin kubunuh dia sekarang,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku harus kabur selagi sempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau kembali ke pasukanku,\Ndan pastikan dia mati nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimanapun caranya!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar biadab.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.54,0:07:57.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pantas saja mudah ditebak.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.59,0:08:03.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makhluk sepertimu selalu\Nmenyembunyikan tipu muslihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.98,0:08:17.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau libatkan semua orang\Ndalam kerusuhan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, kau menertawakan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.40,0:08:22.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sesak napas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Inilah karma atas perbuatanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.20,0:08:28.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.83,0:08:32.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Membusuklah di neraka\Ndan renungkan perbuatanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan menatapku begitu!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.84,0:08:42.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.59,0:08:45.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau mati di sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.85,0:08:52.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa bernapas!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mati? Tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku belum mau mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan mendaki lebih tinggi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.07,0:09:08.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para bedebah yang meremehkanku,\Nkalian pasti akan menelan ludah sendiri!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.21,0:09:21.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat lahir,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.32,0:09:26.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewa memberi manusia satu set kartu\Nyang menentukan hidup seseorang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.09,0:09:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak bisa ditukarkan\Ndengan milik orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.85,0:09:37.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka yang dapat kartu bakat hebat\Nbisa menjalani hidup dengan mudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.69,0:09:45.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, kartu yang kudapat\Nhanyalah kartu biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.82,0:09:50.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak lahir, Dewa sudah berpaling dariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.20,0:09:55.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di Agensi Momotaro,\Nperbedaan itu sangat jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak punya bakat atau kemampuan atletik.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.17,0:10:03.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma Momotaro di bawah rata-rata.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.21,0:10:06.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal pertama yang mereka katakan\Nketika aku bergabung adalah...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.17,0:10:11.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berikan dukungan terbaik dari belakang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.77,0:10:18.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sama saja diberi tahu sejak awal\Nbahwa aku selamanya jadi bawahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.77,0:10:25.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Agen muda berbakat mengejekku,\Nmemanfaatkan, dan merendahkanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.11,0:10:28.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengingat namaku saja mereka tak sudi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.12,0:10:34.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bersumpah, akan kubuat mereka\Ntebus kesombongan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka yang bisa bertarung
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.03,0:10:42.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,melenggang di bawah\Nsorotan lampu tanpa usaha keras.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.92,0:10:46.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dan lihat saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.21,0:10:49.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah berapa kali aku membisikkan\Nitu pada diriku sendiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.26,0:10:55.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuubah rasa iri dan benci pada orang\Nberbakat jadi bahan bakar kekuatanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.31,0:11:00.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ikhlas menerima kemampuanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.35,0:11:04.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana caranya\Nbisa melejit dengan kekuatan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.98,0:11:08.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuajukan permintaan rahasia guna mengasah\Nkemampuanku, berlatih tanpa henti,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.53,0:11:14.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,menambah durasi\Ndan jumlah orang yang kukuasai.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Latihannya brutal.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.16,0:11:20.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu tidurku habis tersita.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, di tengah jalan, aku sadar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.39,0:11:39.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kemampuan ini ada batasnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lemah!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.31,0:11:51.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewa, melihat diriku saja\NEngkau tak sudi, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.91,0:11:58.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, tak peduli sekotor apa tanganku,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.83,0:12:01.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,selama tak ada yang tahu,\Ntidak masalah, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.88,0:12:09.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kulanggar batas demi posisi tinggi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kugunakan semua metode yang kutahu,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.84,0:12:17.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,mencari kelemahan, curi info pribadi,\Ndan memaksa orang berlutut.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.31,0:12:22.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak peduli meski korbankan nyawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.73,0:12:30.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekali tangan ternoda,\Nselamanya tak bisa bersih.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku tak menyesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada jalan lain bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.54,0:12:42.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua usaha itu akhirnya berbuah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.25,0:12:48.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku diangkat jadi kapten,\Npangkat yang mustahil bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Melihat para bajingan yang dulu\Nmeremehkanku, kini membungkuk
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.88,0:12:58.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,adalah perasaan paling nikmat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, aku belum puas.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.77,0:13:08.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kubuat para bedebah itu sadar\Nbetapa bodohnya mereka dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk itu, aku harus naik lebih tinggi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih tinggi dan terus lebih tinggi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah pikirku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.01,0:13:39.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang, aku dikalahkan\Noleh seorang bocah!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Situasinya tak pernah berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.81,0:13:45.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang berbakat selalu menghalangi jalanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.56,0:13:48.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa? Kenapa aku tak berhak?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.03,0:13:59.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bekerja keras tanpa modal bakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.32,0:14:02.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa salahnya kalau menodai\Ntanganku dengan darah?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.62,0:14:09.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku... juga menginginkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bakat alami itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.13,0:14:16.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selanjutnya, takkan berakhir begini!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bersumpah, di kehidupan selanjutnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.81,0:14:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku akan memperoleh
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.77,0:14:35.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,bakat sejati!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.65,0:14:39.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shinya tak sadar,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.99,0:14:44.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,bagi Momotaro lain yang lahir tanpa bakat,\Ndialah simbol harapan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski tanpa kemampuan hebat,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.12,0:14:53.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,keberhasilannya menjadi kapten\Ntelah menginspirasi pengikutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.05,0:14:58.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jalan yang ia lalui\Nmemang bukan yang paling terpuji.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.17,0:15:01.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, dia tak berhenti\Nmelihat lurus ke atas.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.34,0:15:06.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria yang berjuang,\Nmempertanyakan bakat dan kepantasan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.27,0:15:12.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Momoiwa Shinya, tewas pada usia 28 tahun.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pertempuran yang sia-sia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.63,0:15:36.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan bertindak tegas
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.05,0:15:40.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,agar kau mau mendengarkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.38,0:15:43.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak mau dengar omong kosong!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.61,0:15:56.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pakai senjatanya seperti penjungkit?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bocah itu, Mikado, menakjubkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.49,0:16:08.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat bergerak secepat itu,\Ndia masih bisa membidik Ichinose.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.25,0:16:16.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.75,0:16:18.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kontrol banyak senjata,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia antisipasi gerakan Ichinose
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menghadang sebelum ia menjangkaunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.51,0:16:30.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan kata lain, dia tak bisa lari.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terjebak!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus kutambah kekuatannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.74,0:16:50.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengontrol banyak senjata\Ndi usia semuda itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.54,0:16:52.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,bahkan bisa sesuaikan kekuatannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.71,0:16:55.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pasti lahir dengan\Nnaluri pembunuh spesial.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.42,0:16:59.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang seperti itu disebut Anak Ajaib.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.84,0:17:04.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau terus begini, senjataku bisa hancur.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.59,0:17:07.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus bergerak,\Nbuat senjata lagi mumpung sempat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mati langkah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.31,0:17:15.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin kekuatannya belum cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Celaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.82,0:17:26.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah! Aku terlalu berlebihan!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.74,0:17:32.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dibanding Mikado, kontrol Ichinose\Natas kekuatannya sangat ceroboh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.16,0:17:36.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus menembak begitu,\Nkau akan kehabisan darah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa seranganku kena?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.84,0:17:44.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia menghilang?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke mana dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lemah, Ichinose.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kalah telak.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.16,0:18:12.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ichinose tak mungkin menang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.00,0:18:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, itu kekuatan penyembuhan Oni.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.01,0:18:28.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sialan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.30,0:18:32.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sama-sama pakai senjata,\Ntapi aku cuma bisa wujudkan satu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.85,0:18:34.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.97,0:18:38.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kukira aku cuma bisa\Nwujudkan satu senjata?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.10,0:18:44.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika Mikado bisa, aku juga pasti bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.32,0:18:51.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bodoh! Selama ini aku terus\Nhambat kemampuanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.20,0:18:58.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perbedaan kekuatan kami sudah jelas, tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,api di matanya belum padam?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.96,0:19:07.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.34,0:19:09.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,seperti Mikado.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.47,0:19:13.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, wujudlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.39,0:19:15.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo! Ayo! Ayo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sialan, wujudlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.64,0:19:22.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sedang apa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.94,0:19:23.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Celaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hampir saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tak berhasil?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu senjata lancar saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sialan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana caranya?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.76,0:19:49.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pikirkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, berpikirlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.05,0:19:52.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pikirkan, sialan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:53.89,0:19:56.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat! Aku tak tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.56,0:20:00.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sialan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus membalasnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.94,0:20:07.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyusun strategi\Nbukanlah keunggulan Ichinose.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.16,0:20:14.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.96,0:20:24.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertahan dan mengecoh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.08,0:20:27.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.60,0:20:47.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akui saja kekalahanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.94,0:20:52.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau akui, demi masa lalu kita,\Naku akan membunuhmu dengan cepat.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.32,0:20:58.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.00,0:21:06.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Batu ini berbentuk pistol.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada rotan, akar pun jadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tersenyum.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.38,0:21:14.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa rencananya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.39,0:21:19.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terasa pas di tanganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.18,0:21:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, senjataku tetap satu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.48,0:21:26.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa bedanya aku dan Mikado?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.85,0:21:28.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dia melakukannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.36,0:21:33.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah apa yang kau lakukan, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.17,0:21:49.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Enam senjata?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.42,0:21:57.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau sungguh hebat, Mikado.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.93,0:22:02.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika kau tak mau mengaku kalah,\Nkau akan hancur berkeping-keping.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.02,0:22:04.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak sudi!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.60,0:22:10.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua tuduhanmu salah paham!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:18.74,0:22:20.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau keras kepala!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.03,0:22:23.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga sama saja!
